IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
PROGRAM-ID. FUTUREVAL.

DATA DIVISION.
WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
    01 WS-PRINCIPAL-IN        PIC 9(7)V99.
    01 WS-RATE-IN             PIC 9(2)V999.
    01 WS-PERIODS-IN          PIC 9(3).
    
    01 WS-PRINCIPAL           PIC S9(7)V99 COMP-3.
    01 WS-RATE                PIC S9(2)V999 COMP-3.
    01 WS-PERIODS             PIC S9(3)    COMP-3.
    01 WS-FUTURE-VALUE        PIC S9(9)V99 COMP-3.
    01 WS-COUNTER             PIC S9(3)    COMP-3.

    01 WS-DISPLAY-PRINCIPAL   PIC $$,$$$,$$9.99.
    01 WS-DISPLAY-FUTURE-VAL  PIC $$,$$$,$$$,$$9.99.

PROCEDURE DIVISION.
MAIN-LOGIC.
    DISPLAY "Enter Principal Amount (e.g., 10000.00): " WITH NO ADVANCING.
    ACCEPT WS-PRINCIPAL-IN.
    DISPLAY "Enter Annual Interest Rate (e.g., 5.25 for 5.25%): " WITH NO ADVANCING.
    ACCEPT WS-RATE-IN.
    DISPLAY "Enter Number of Periods (Years): " WITH NO ADVANCING.
    ACCEPT WS-PERIODS-IN.

    MOVE WS-PRINCIPAL-IN TO WS-PRINCIPAL.
    MOVE WS-RATE-IN      TO WS-RATE.
    MOVE WS-PERIODS-IN   TO WS-PERIODS.

    MOVE WS-PRINCIPAL    TO WS-FUTURE-VALUE.

    PERFORM VARYING WS-COUNTER FROM 1 BY 1
        UNTIL WS-COUNTER > WS-PERIODS
        COMPUTE WS-FUTURE-VALUE = WS-FUTURE-VALUE * (1 + (WS-RATE / 100))
    END-PERFORM.

    MOVE WS-PRINCIPAL    TO WS-DISPLAY-PRINCIPAL.
    MOVE WS-FUTURE-VALUE TO WS-DISPLAY-FUTURE-VAL.
    
    DISPLAY "Initial Principal: " WS-DISPLAY-PRINCIPAL.
    DISPLAY "Future Value:    " WS-DISPLAY-FUTURE-VAL.
    
    STOP RUN.
